Why is that?

00:05:20.933 --> 00:05:22.475
AUDIENCE: Because
the people who made

00:05:22.475 --> 00:05:23.933
the acronym
[? like making their ?]

00:05:23.933 --> 00:05:26.315
acronyms, and [INAUDIBLE]
bullfrog was not [INAUDIBLE]..

00:05:26.315 --> 00:05:28.690
MICHAEL SHORT: So actually
bullfrog stands for something.

