who took extreme offense
to this detriment

00:05:51.140 --> 00:05:52.900
to nuclear power
plants being attributed

00:05:52.900 --> 00:05:54.668
to his fine laboratory.

00:05:54.668 --> 00:05:56.710
MICHAEL AMES: Oh, I thought
it was chromium-rich.

00:05:56.710 --> 00:05:58.377
MICHAEL SHORT: Oh,
see, that would work,

00:05:58.377 --> 00:06:00.310
but they're not
actually chromium-rich.

00:06:00.310 --> 00:06:00.950
Yeah.

00:06:00.950 --> 00:06:01.450
Cool.

