I work over at the
Nuclear Reactor Lab mostly

00:06:14.330 --> 00:06:19.320
doing nuclear experiments, but
I also run the NAA lab there.

00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:21.200
And I've been doing
it for a while.

00:06:21.200 --> 00:06:25.620
So the idea-- the reason
we've got these guys,

00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:29.060
it'll irradiate the
samples in this.

