something gets radiated in
this, I slip the top off,

00:06:37.730 --> 00:06:40.620
and you probably can't see that,
but it's for a little poly bag.

00:06:40.620 --> 00:06:43.790
I'll dump your sample
into the poly bag.

00:06:43.790 --> 00:06:47.320
So it's something that's like
one piece that works the best.

