I mean, are you guys can
be able to come to the lab

00:09:16.770 --> 00:09:17.788
when we do the shorts?

00:09:17.788 --> 00:09:19.580
MICHAEL SHORT: Depends
on when you do them.

00:09:19.580 --> 00:09:21.640
If it's early
November, then yes.

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:22.850
MICHAEL AMES: Yeah, OK.

